Real men shed tears for this kind of thing!

45
00:03:11,224 --> 00:03:15,194
Awesome! Awesome! Awesome!
Awesome! Awesome!

46
00:03:15,195 --> 00:03:17,155
Hey, wait! Wait up!

47
