Damn it!

48
00:03:24,337 --> 00:03:25,947
Stop! Stop already!

49
00:03:30,277 --> 00:03:31,977
Hello, Misato.

50
00:03:31,978 --> 00:03:34,280
How have you been?

51
00:03:34,281 --> 00:03:37,049
Fine. How about you?
You've grown some, haven't you?

52
00:03:37,050 --> 00:03:41,620
Yeah! I'm not just taller,
my figure's filled out as well.

53
00:03:41,621 --> 00:03:42,988
Let me introduce you.

54
00:03:42,989 --> 00:03:47,359
This is the pilot of Evangelion Unit 02,
the Second Child,

55
00:03:47,360 --> 00:03:49,090
Asuka Langley Sohryu.

56
00:03:51,765 --> 00:03:52,263
Episode 8

57
00:03:52,265 --> 00:03:52,765
Episode 8
Asuka

58
00:03:52,766 --> 00:03:53,726
Episode 8
Asuka Arrives in Japan

59
00:03:54,201 --> 00:03:55,491
What did you do that for?!

60
00:03:57,637 --> 00:04:00,106
That's the viewing fee.
Quite a bargain, don't you think?

61
00:04:00,107 --> 00:04:03,267
