Oh no, thank you for giving me the
opportunity to baby-sit some kids.

71
00:04:37,744 --> 00:04:42,448
We appreciate your assistance
in the transport of Unit 02.

72
00:04:42,449 --> 00:04:45,199
Here are the specs for the
emergency power supply socket.

73
00:04:46,720 --> 00:04:51,720
In the first place, I haven't heard anything
about activating that toy while at sea.

74
00:04:51,792 --> 00:04:56,395
Why don't you just think of this as
being prepared for an emergency?

75
00:04:56,396 --> 00:05:01,396
That's why the Pacific Fleet is escorting it.

76
00:05:01,601 --> 00:05:05,704
When did the UN Navy
become a cargo service?

77
00:05:05,705 --> 00:05:09,842
It believe it was just after a certain
organization was established.

78
00:05:09,843 --> 00:05:12,945
Quite a grandiose escort for
transporting one single toy!

79
00:05:12,946 --> 00:05:15,281
After all, this is the entire Pacific Fleet.

80
00:05:15,282 --> 00:05:18,984
It's still not enough, considering
the importance of the Eva.

81
00:05:18,985 --> 00:05:20,786
Would you sign this document?

82
00:05:20,787 --> 00:05:24,123
Not yet. Eva Unit 02 and its pilot
have been entrusted to us

83
00:05:24,124 --> 00:05:27,059
by the Third Branch in Germany.

84
00:05:27,060 --> 00:05:29,295
You can't just do as you please!

85
00:05:29,296 --> 00:05:31,163
Then, when will you transfer them to us?

86
00:05:31,164 --> 00:05:33,966
Once we've unloaded in New Yokosuka.

87
00:05:33,967 --> 00:05:36,702
The ocean is our jurisdiction.

88
00:05:36,703 --> 00:05:38,637
You will follow our orders here.

89
00:05:38,638 --> 00:05:40,272
I understand.

90
00:05:40,273 --> 00:05:43,242
However, I should remind you that,
in the case of an emergency,

91
00:05:43,243 --> 00:05:46,011
Nerv's authority overrides yours.

92
00:05:46,012 --> 00:05:47,680
She's cool!

93
00:05:47,681 --> 00:05:49,215
She's practically like Miss Ritsuko.

94
00:05:49,216 --> 00:05:51,784
You're as gallant as ever.

95
00:05:51,785 --> 00:05:52,805
Kaji!

96
00:05:55,255 --> 00:05:58,424
Mr. Kaji, I don't recall inviting you
onto the bridge.

97
00:05:58,425 --> 00:05:59,655
Oh, sorry about that.

98
00:06:00,193 --> 00:06:01,293
Excuse us, then. We're counting on you to
escort us to New Yokosuka as ordered.

99
00:06:01,294 --> 00:06:03,495
This is a date?
